    "bio": "ScoutNow is an AI-powered competitor tracking tool that monitors websites, social media, and other digital channels to deliver real-time insights into your competitors’ strategies. It automates competitive research, highlights key developments such as pricing changes or product launches, and delivers actionable recommendations directly to your inbox.",
